Package: DeepSeekCell
Title: Ontology-Guided LLM Cell Type Annotation for Single-Cell RNA-seq
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-11
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mohamed", "Kone", role = "aut"),
    person("Shulin", "Wang", email = "books@hnu.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Hunan University", role = "cph")
  )
Author: Mohamed Kone [aut], Shulin Wang [aut, cre], Hunan University [cph]
Maintainer: Shulin Wang <books@hnu.edu.cn>
Description: Provides an ontology-guided large language model framework and
    interactive Shiny platform for explainable cell type annotation in
    single-cell RNA sequencing. The package converts cluster marker genes into
    standardized, confidence-scored annotations, maps labels to the Cell
    Ontology, validates result quality, exports reports, and supports
    reproducible benchmarking against established annotation methods.
